DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Can you tell me about Ashenfall?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Can you tell me about Ashenfall?

Message.SourceString: I'm Zanik, I'm a cave goblin. Sort of like the goblins over there in Bramblemead village... only we chose a peace over violence.
Message.LocalizedString: I'm Zanik, I'm a cave goblin. Sort of like the goblins over there in Bramblemead village... only we chose a peace over violence.

Message.SourceString: Fortunately, we've got magic! As you improve in a skill you'll discover spells that you can use, such as my favourite - Axtral Projection.
Message.LocalizedString: Fortunately, we've got magic! As you improve in a skill you'll discover spells that you can use, such as my favourite - Axtral Projection.

Message.SourceString: I wonder why they're not in the history books.
Message.LocalizedString: I wonder why they're not in the history books.

Message.SourceString: Axtral projection will let you slice down trees with a wave of your fingers. Much less time consuming than the lumberjack gig.
Message.LocalizedString: Axtral projection will let you slice down trees with a wave of your fingers. Much less time consuming than the lumberjack gig.

Message.SourceString: But, magic comes at a cost -- runes. You'll need both air and astral runes to cast Axtral projection, so here's how to get them.
Message.LocalizedString: But, magic comes at a cost -- runes. You'll need both air and astral runes to cast Axtral projection, so here's how to get them.

Message.SourceString: See those geysers around, with the floating rocks? Take this pickaxe and mine some essence from them, build a rune altar and then craft the runes from rune essence.
Message.LocalizedString: See those geysers around, with the floating rocks? Take this pickaxe and mine some essence from them, build a rune altar and then craft the runes from rune essence.

Message.SourceString: As well as goblins, look at the creatures here. So vibrant and full of life. This whole place feels... magical.
Message.LocalizedString: As well as goblins, look at the creatures here. So vibrant and full of life. This whole place feels... magical.

Message.SourceString: The interesting thing about Ashenfall is that it's laced with magic. Anima everywhere, pouring out of the ground. Which we can use to our advantage.
Message.LocalizedString: The interesting thing about Ashenfall is that it's laced with magic. Anima everywhere, pouring out of the ground. Which we can use to our advantage.

Message.SourceString: Here, I'll show you. First, let's look at things without magic to help you. I need you to cut down a couple of trees and bring me some ash logs. Simple, right?
Message.LocalizedString: Here, I'll show you. First, let's look at things without magic to help you. I need you to cut down a couple of trees and bring me some ash logs. Simple, right?

Message.SourceString: Oh wow, bit of a packrat are we? You're carrying too much right now, come back and chat with me when you've cleared some space from your backpack.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh wow, bit of a packrat are we? You're carrying too much right now, come back and chat with me when you've cleared some space from your backpack.

Message.SourceString: About fifty ash logs should do it, so make sure you've got a well maintained axe. Shouldn't take too long, come back to me when you have them.
Message.LocalizedString: About fifty ash logs should do it, so make sure you've got a well maintained axe. Shouldn't take too long, come back to me when you have them.

Message.SourceString: Cut down trees and gather 50 ash logs, then bring them to me.
Message.LocalizedString: Cut down trees and gather 50 ash logs, then bring them to me.

Message.SourceString: Great, you've got them. Now, between you and me, that was a bit repetitive right? I'd be exhausted having to do that all the time.
Message.LocalizedString: Great, you've got them. Now, between you and me, that was a bit repetitive right? I'd be exhausted having to do that all the time.

Message.SourceString: There are goblins here, that's unexpected. I thought I knew about all the tribes, but there's a whole load of them here.
Message.LocalizedString: There are goblins here, that's unexpected. I thought I knew about all the tribes, but there's a whole load of them here.

Message.SourceString: Most of my people stay underground, hiding from the surface. But I couldn't wait to explore this vast and wonderful world.
Message.LocalizedString: Most of my people stay underground, hiding from the surface. But I couldn't wait to explore this vast and wonderful world.

Message.SourceString: I'm regretting it a bit, what with big scary dragons and all, but I'm excited too. Looking forward to learn everything about this place.
Message.LocalizedString: I'm regretting it a bit, what with big scary dragons and all, but I'm excited too. Looking forward to learn everything about this place.

Message.SourceString: Dragons, it had to be dragons. Oh, hi, sorry, nice to meet you, I'm Zanik. I'm the local survival and goblin expert around here.
Message.LocalizedString: Dragons, it had to be dragons. Oh, hi, sorry, nice to meet you, I'm Zanik. I'm the local survival and goblin expert around here.

Message.SourceString: Vannaka was looking for you, mentioned something about fine dining?
Message.LocalizedString: Vannaka was looking for you, mentioned something about fine dining?

Message.SourceString: I think someone is looking for you. Mentioned a task they needed you to complete. Check your map for where to find them.
Message.LocalizedString: I think someone is looking for you. Mentioned a task they needed you to complete. Check your map for where to find them.

Message.SourceString: A new adventure is always exciting, don't you think? We lost some good people... friends... but we need to push forward, in their memory.
Message.LocalizedString: A new adventure is always exciting, don't you think? We lost some good people... friends... but we need to push forward, in their memory.
